(44, 0, 2, 0, 5, 'JAMUR KRISPY', 'keripik-jamur', 'pcs', 10000, 0, 20000, '100', 'HHBK-KPH_TANAH_LAUT(JAMUR_TIRAM_KRISPY).png', 'Jamur tiram adalah jamur pangan dari kelompok Basidiomycota dan termasuk kelas Homobasidiomycetes. Salah satu olahan pangan dari jamur tiram ini adalah Jamur Krispy Syifa yang menjadi salah satu produk unggulan dari KTH Subur Makmur yang berada di Desa Telaga Kecamatan Pelaihari Kabupaten Tanah Laut.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Jamur tiram</span></b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;(</span><i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus ostreatus</span></i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">) adalah&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamur_pangan\" title=\"Jamur pangan\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">jamur pangan</span></a><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;dari kelompok&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basidiomycota\" title=\"Basidiomycota\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Basidiomycota</span></a><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;dan termasuk kelas&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Homobasidiomycetes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" title=\"Homobasidiomycetes (halaman belum tersedia)\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Homobasidiomycetes</span></a><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;dengan ciri-ciri umum tubuh buah berwarna\r\nputih hingga krem dan tudungnya berbentuk setengah lingkaran mirip cangkang&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiram\" title=\"Tiram\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">tiram</span></a><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;dengan bagian tengah agak cekung.</span><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> Jamur\r\ntiram masih satu kerabat dengan&nbsp;</span></span><i><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pleurotus_eryngii\" title=\"Pleurotus eryngii\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus eryngii</span></a></i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;dan sering dikenal dengan sebutan&nbsp;</span><i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">King Oyster Mushroom</span></i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Tak hanya nikmat dikonsumsi, ada beragam manfaat\r\njamur tiram yang baik untuk kesehatan. Jamur berwarna putih ini diketahui\r\nmengandung beragam nutrisi yang dapat menjaga daya tahan tubuh dan melindungi\r\ntubuh dari berbagai penyakit.</span></span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://sisdh.kalselprov.go.id/asset/images/jamur.PNG\" style=\"width: 461.5px; height: 307.667px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"><br></span></span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"><br></span><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Ketika berbicara tentang jamur tiram, Anda mungkin langsung\r\nmembayangkan&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.alodokter.com/kandungan-nutrisi-dan-manfaat-jamur-untuk-mencegah-penyakit\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">jamur</span></a><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;yang diolah menjadi&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">jamur crispy</span></em><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;atau tumis jamur. Jamur tiram (</span><em><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus ostreatus</span></em><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">) memang kerap digunakan sebagai bahan dasar\r\nberbagai jenis masakan, karena rasanya yang lezat dan kaya akan nutrisi.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Dalam sekitar 100 gram\r\njamur tiram terdapat 18 kalori. Hal ini membuat jamur tiram sebagai bahan\r\nmakanan yang tergolong rendah kalori. Selain rendah kalori, jamur tiram juga\r\nmengandung nutrisi penting yang bermanfaat untuk kesehatan tubuh, seperti:</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Protein</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Karbohidrat</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Serat</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxS