um, kalium,&nbsp;</span><i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">zinc</span></i><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">, dan\r\nselenium</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Tak hanya itu, jamur\r\ntiram juga mengandung beragam antioksidan yang berperan dalam mencegah penyakit\r\nkronis dalam tubuh.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Sehingga, selain lezat\r\nuntuk dikonsumsi para konsumen juga mendapatkan banyak manfaat dan khasiat dari\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Jamur Krispy Syifa</span></b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> olahan dari Kelompok\r\nTani Hutan Subur Makmur Binaan dari KPH Tanah Laut ini.</span></span></p>', '5', 'Y', '', 23, 1, 0, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', ''),
