(145, 0, 2, 0, 5, 'BRIKET ARANG', 'briket-arang-091702', 'pcs', 5000, 0, 10000, '500', 'HHBK-KPH_TANAH_LAUT(BRIKET_ARANG).jpg', 'Briket arang diproduksi oleh kelompok tani hutan binaan KPH Tanah Laut yaitu, KTH Batu Kura yang terletak di Desa Galam Kecamatan Bajuin Kabupaten Tanah Laut.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"https://sisdh.kalselprov.go.id/asset/images/HHBK-KPH_TANAH_LAUT(BRIKET_ARANG).jpg\" style=\"width: 383px; height: 255.461px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Briket arang</span></b><span style=\"font-family: \"Times New Roman\", \"serif\"; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \"Times New Roman\";\">merupakan bahan bakar padat yang mengandung karbon,\r\nmempunyai nilai kalori yang tinggi, dan dapat menyala dalam waktu yang lama.\r\nBioarang adalah</span><b><span style=\"font-family: \"Times New Roman\";\">arang</span></b><span style=\"font-family: \"Times New Roman\";\">yang diperoleh d